name: Organic Baby Lotion
description:
Baby Beanie Organic Baby Lotion smells delicate and is perfect for both mums and bubs

 

Tahitian Beauty Pty Ltd is a boutique business located at Springfield Lakes, Queensland.

We manufacture a range of body and baby care products that we can supply to customers throughout Australia.

Our goal is to provide high quality products that are made from botanical ingredients wherever possible so that they are gentle on the skin, invigorating to the senses and kind to the environment.

Our unique range of Mummy’s and Baby care products are made by using blends of certified organic vegetable oils, coco, shea, mango butter, essential oils.

We have selected these ingredients to provide customers with high quality products that assist with retaining and rehydrating the skin’s natural moisture content.

Key Ingredients

* Goats Milk

* Certified organic coco butter

* Organic oatmeal

* Zinc

* Lavender Essential Oil

* Tangerine Essential Oil
